\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Hananiah commanded his son, “See that I am dying because of Jeremiah, and he made me a liar in my 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ prophecy. If you can cause him to stumble, cause him to stumble. And his son commanded his son also 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ in that manner, and when the time came, he caused him to stumble.  
